backend/jarvis_backend/wake/detector.py

    The streaming melspectrogram / speech-embedding buffer logic mirrors
    openWakeWord's `openwakeword.utils.AudioFeatures`, reimplemented against
    onnxruntime so the shipped sidecar does not depend on scipy or
    scikit-learn. Scores match the reference implementation.

