================================================================================
Models downloaded at run time (scripts/fetch_models.py)
================================================================================

No model weights are contained in this repository. `scripts/fetch_models.py` is
user-invoked and fetches each file from its upstream source over pinned URLs
with SHA-256 verification. The licenses below are the upstream terms and apply
to the downloaded files, not to this repository's source code.

Wake word — openWakeWord v0.5.1 release assets
    melspectrogram.onnx, embedding_model.onnx, hey_jarvis_v0.1.onnx
    https://github.com/dscripka/openWakeWord
    openWakeWord's pre-trained models are distributed under Creative Commons
    Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0),
    because datasets with unknown or restrictive licensing were used in
    training. The shared speech-embedding backbone originates from Google's
    `speech_embedding` TFHub module, published under Apache-2.0.
    https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/

    NOTE: the NonCommercial term belongs to these downloaded weights, not to
    JARVIS itself. Anyone intending commercial use should replace the wake-word
    model — `scripts/train_wake_word.py` trains a drop-in replacement offline.

